{"tid":1687422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國民調指國民對應否彈劾特朗普並逼他下台意見分歧","createTime":"2019-11-01T22:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T23:28:43.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"245b0c38187a15a15a0ae56d57d99b5e559db787","tid":1687422,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T22:33:16.000Z","msg":"美國國會眾議院議長波洛西，拒絕透露眾議院正式表決彈劾總統特朗普的時間表，又說會繼續盤問證人，預計本月傳召多名證人公開作證。<br />\n<br />\n波洛西接受當地電視台訪問時，形容對特朗普展開彈劾調查，對國家而言是可悲的事，因為沒有在國會工作的人，想將目標定在彈劾總統，但強調行動是別無選擇。<br />\n<br />\n根據《美國廣播公司》及《華盛頓郵報》的最新聯合民調，美國國民對應否彈劾特朗普而逼他下台，意見分歧，有49%受訪者支持國會彈劾，反對的有48%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489621-20191102.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489621-20191102.htm&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8Kzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=54ee3ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489621-20191102.htm&h=850f68fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489621-20191102.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c5ba3de75f6e122d2555f8a03def12329bbdf9dd","tid":1687422,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T22:44:02.000Z","msg":"中國人：民主就係咁亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3685a47fc50ffd2b2431458ee7128cd4df26ee6d","tid":1687422,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:28:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋到點解trump由原本全美國政界最強硬，變成最軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n彈劾la diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}